* EZT program with no explicit END-JOB or END-REPORT
FILE CUSTFILE DISK 80
CUSTNO    1   5   N
CUSTNAME  6  30   A
BALANCE  36  10   P 2
STATUS   46   1   A

DEFINE WS-TOTAL N 12 VALUE 0

JOB INPUT CUSTFILE

  IF STATUS EQ 'A'
    ADD BALANCE TO WS-TOTAL
    DISPLAY CUSTNO CUSTNAME BALANCE
  END-IF

REPORT CUSTRPT
  TITLE 'CUSTOMER BALANCE REPORT'
  PRINT CUSTNO CUSTNAME BALANCE
